{"tid":1154082,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"逆線司機亂咁行　囂張唔認錯︰地下冇寫喎！","createTime":"2019-05-14T05:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T13:12:40.000Z","uid":225464,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"53a5926247af4e5d868c5832a479e2214f3e6e00","tid":1154082,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:03:42.000Z","msg":"逆線司機亂咁行 囂張唔認錯︰地下冇寫喎！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2E6Ld1f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2E6Ld1f&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=a735fb71\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2E6Ld1f</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190514/photo/bkn-20190514123323802-0514_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190514125933\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190514%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190514123323802-0514_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190514125933&h=ef8d5eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地下冇寫就可以任駛？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民Wilber Chong上傳片段至Facebook群組「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」，只見周日（12日）晚上約9時半，他正駛離鳳攸北街附近的錶位停車場，未料有橙色私家車突然迎頭逆線駛至。<br />\n<br />\n他見狀隨即提醒︰「你知唔知你逆線呀？單線嚟㗎。」惟逆線司機聞言辯稱︰「條線喺邊度呀？冇寫喎地下。」他慨嘆︰「好心提你，你仲要鬧人」。"},{"pid":"05974cafd7a4c5e4efc07d6e94cee3ae67429082","tid":1154082,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"又有乜問題？<br />\n<br />\n不嬲法例冇寫都做得<br />\n<br />\n留名睇連登畜生挑戰常識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78136465357cbaa5954d222460f4b47060b65ce","tid":1154082,"uid":241536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"05974cafd7a4c5e4efc07d6e94cee3ae67429082","tid":1154082,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"又有乜問題？<br />\n<br />\n不嬲法例冇寫都做得<br />\n<br />\n留名睇連登畜生挑戰常識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"地下冇寫，但係一定有路牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.